{"tid":2222970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖] 有昔日既販民，先有之後本土既梁天琦","createTime":"2020-09-29T12:39:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T12:45:41.000Z","uid":188515,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5293a22baeec74be704c87db4c800f488f869b86","tid":2222970,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:39:39.000Z","msg":"今日成班販民主派宣佈接受共產黨既委任<br />\n自行延任一年，愧對選民對佢哋嘅信任<br />\n但亦因為呢一次，令大部份人睇撚清你班仆街既所作所為<br />\n只係一班成利益而出賣香港人既政棍<br />\n仲要好意思話要議會抗爭，誓要爭取五大訴求<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xwHbFbE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxwHbFbE.jpg&h=f5949fcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而佢地出賣香港既行徑，亦必招致失敗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KmXV6SD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKmXV6SD.jpg&h=3b79baaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n他朝一日，本土亦會隨之抬頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rFmWRjo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrFmWRjo.jpg&h=d9c8c75f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而我地要思考既下一步<br />\n就係點樣重新分配資源，開闢另一條新戰線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dCPNdyC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdCPNdyC.jpg&h=5bd335e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而我地亦必須要認清楚，議會戰線經已一早崩潰<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dnUJwjO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdnUJwjO.jpg&h=89804be9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2jDqKET.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2jDqKET.jpg&h=0450ce26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再唔能夠投放過多既資源係已經無太大功效既議會上<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bz8Fyyq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbz8Fyyq.jpg&h=a2d83c7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁可能你地就會問<br />\n錦鋰有咩高見<br />\n答案係無，事實上要靠大家一齊思索<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ps17X0M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fps17X0M.jpg&h=0058e271&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JrNK0d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJrNK0d9.jpg&h=c35db0fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而我地亦必須要汲取歷史教訓，好好裝備自己<br />\n一齊譜寫真正屬於香港人既歷史<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r1z5KF4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr1z5KF4.jpg&h=d945a20c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb9284a06086c4b0244c2a140a332ce2f02c5d09","tid":2222970,"uid":188515,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:40:16.000Z","msg":"We Shall Never Surrender!<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B5PH7XlgFWc&amp;t=3s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DB5PH7XlgFWc%26t%3D3s&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXIoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=14662b54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B5PH7XlgFWc&amp;t=3s</a>"},{"pid":"089ce5943673ffcc921ff3748a884e2b658db084","tid":2222970,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:41:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a7614e4d45fe8bc1c037d55e0c49871e624d39f3","tid":2222970,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:41:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6bb1723a3c2dfae621ddbb443085c2d939bfa100","tid":2222970,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:42:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"449abafe3a29894ce8d194fffe3e181d29e01746","tid":2222970,"uid":188515,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:43:33.000Z","msg":"孫文的野望<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XRT2CXKzEMc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXRT2CXKzEMc&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXIoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=3d1c53a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XRT2CXKzEMc</a>"},{"pid":"85babd24c1ec0ba628a912078274c0ac98035b1a","tid":2222970,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:45:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}],"pinned":{"pid":"449abafe3a29894ce8d194fffe3e181d29e01746","tid":2222970,"uid":188515,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T12:43:33.000Z","msg":"孫文的野望<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XRT2CXKzEMc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXRT2CXKzEMc&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXIoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=3d1c53a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XRT2CXKzEMc</a>"}}